predictions.article: US farmers face higher costs, fewer markets from tariffs
predictions.prediction: The imposition of tariffs on agricultural inputs and retaliatory tariffs from China will lead to a 10% increase in U.S. food prices within the next month.

predictions.article: China hits U.S. agriculture, says it won't be bullied by fresh Trump tariffs
predictions.prediction: U.S. soybean exports to China will decrease by at least 90% within the next month due to the new tariffs.
